的猫或狗经常留下不想要的惊喜，您可能需要寻找其他地方。它的声音也比 j7 等较新（如果效果较差）的选项更大。不过，以这个价格来说，这是一个简单的选择——您将获得高效的清洁服务，从而腾出时间来处理更重要的任务。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/irobots-roomba-s9-robot-vacuum-is-back-down-to-a-record-low-price-152658325.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/irobots-roomba-s9-robot-vacuum-is-back-down-to-a-record-low-price-152658325.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 24232f63-5311-4045-8f10-8d4cc544f010</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 15:26:58 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690557184</ingested><modified> 2023-07-28T15:13:08+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Hobbies & Personal Activities]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/766cd210-2d54-11ee-9dbd-8391aa3e3358" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/766cd210-2d54-11ee-9dbd-8391aa3e3358" width="1920"><media:media_html